FBIS4-8023 "dreeu068_i_94001" FBIS-EEU-94-068 Daily Report 7 Apr 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA One-Day Cease-Fire Agreed Throughout Republic One-Day Cease-Fire Agreed Throughout Republic AU0704172594 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in Serbo-Croatian 1700 GMT 7 Apr 94 AU0704172594 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network Serbo-Croatian BFN [Text] Before a more in-depth look at the news of the day, let us listen to the information that we have just obtained from our fax machine, which says: As the B-H PRESS news agency has learned, an agreement on a one-day cease-fire has been reached with the enemy side this afternoon. [Words indistinct] cease-fire comes in force at 1800 today and refers to the entire territory of Bosnia-Herzegovina. The aim of this cease-fire is to create, with the mediation of UN Protection Force, the conditions for talks and intensification of the peace [word indistinct].
